thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Kandi Quint

author: Kandi Quint
title: Kandi Quint
text: I ordered two boxes for both and of my nephews for their birthdays. I got confirmation that one boxed shipped but nothing for the other box. Taylor took the time to find my box and made me feel at ease that both boxes would ( which they were) delivered together. My nephews told me that this is the best present they got for their birthdays. Thank you lucky tackle box and abig thank u to Taylor for all of his help.
